- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on studying interactions on a social network platform, namely Instagram. 
- cs.SOC (Social and Behavioral Sciences) is also a likely category as the paper investigates political debates and interactions on a social network. 
- cs.CYBER (Cybersecurity and Privacy) is a possible category as the paper touches upon the dissemination of rumors on online social networks. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper analyzes Instagram posts and their engagement metrics (likes and comments). 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper may use natural language processing techniques to analyze the content of comments.
